  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "19 \u0b86\u0bb5\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc8 \u0bb5\u0bc6\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc8\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc1\u0bb4\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbe\u0b95 \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0b8e\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0bb3\u0bc7\u0ba9\u0bcd - \u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "I look forward to full implementation of the 19th Amendment very soon - President Ranil",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "A space will be reserved in Vikaramadevi Park to continue the 'Go Home Run' campaign without any hindrance.",
        "President Ranil Wickremesinghe has mentioned to the party leaders that the 19th amendment of the constitution brought by the good governance government will be re-enforced very soon.",
        "Leader of Opposition Sajith Premadasha urged the President to strengthen the system of parliamentary committees so as to create national consensus without giving ministerial posts to political opportunists.",
        "President Ranil Wickremesinghe took the oath of office on the 21st Thursday at the Parliament Buildings and attended the event and engaged in talks with political party leaders.",
        "Ranil Wickremesinghe party leader meeting that the president expects to deliver his government's policy speech by adjourning Parliament for 24 hours and resuming; Mentioned.",
        "The protestors who have gathered at Kalimugathidal will be given space in Vikaramadevi Park to continue their 'Go Home Run' protest without any hindrance.",
        "In addition, President Ranil Wickremesinghe has urged the party leaders to fully implement the 19th Amendment of the Constitution brought by the Good Governance Government very soon.",
        "Leader of Opposition Sajith Premadasha urged the President to strengthen the system of parliamentary committees so as to create national consensus without giving ministerial posts to political opportunists.",
        "The new government should be formed with the participation of all the political parties that are members of the Parliament. If the economic crisis facing the country is to be resolved, the country's political stability must be maintained and peace must prevail.",
        "Political parties have their own policies, and the policy of one party is sometimes accepted or rejected by another party.",
        "In the present environment, I have called upon all the parties to act beyond the party principles.",
        "Politically, the best change expected by the people should be brought forward through the Parliament. All political parties should cooperate for that.",
        "The President mentioned to the party leaders that it is expected that the basic problems in the social structure will be solved in a couple of months."
      ],
